Package com.hawkejo.complexnumberfft

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FreqObservable
    An observable interface for frequencies.
    FreqObserver
    An observer interface to check for new frequency data.
    FrequencyGenerator
    An interface for an arbitrary class that computes a frequency from an array of doubles
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComplexNumber
    Defines a complex number and allows for math operations on it
    FFTFreqGen
    Computes frequencies from ComplexNumber objects
    FFTMerge
    Performs the merge of a FFT algorithm in its own thread.
    FFTSeparator
    Performs the initial FFT separation in the background
    FFTThread
    Performs an FFT in its own thread.
    Main
    The driver program for testing all of the frequency generation classes
